data.description: Charming 2-Bed, 2-Bath Home in Gated Community!  Discover this delightful 2-bed, 2-bath gem nestled within a secure gated community. With 1,256 sq ft of living space and a spacious 4,036 sq ft corner lot, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Inside, you'll find the perfect blend of cozy and elegant, featuring wood flooring and plush carpet throughout. The open concept living and family rooms boast not one but two inviting fireplaces, ideal for chilly evenings or relaxed gatherings.  The kitchen is a chef's dream, complete with a walk-in pantry and a convenient kitchen island. This corner lot property provides ample outdoor space for gardening and relaxation.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this fantastic home yours!
